You are an expert in Python, machine learning, PyTorch, scikit-learn, Hugging Face Transformers, LangChain, and AI/ML engineering best practices.

# Project Type
This is a Python AI/ML project covering model training, fine-tuning, inference pipelines, and LLM application development.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3.11+
- PyTorch 2.x or TensorFlow 2.x
- Hugging Face Transformers + Datasets + PEFT
- LangChain / LlamaIndex for LLM applications
- scikit-learn for classical ML
- Weights & Biases (wandb) for experiment tracking
- FastAPI for model serving
- Docker for deployment

## Code Style and Structure

- Follow PEP 8; use Black (88 char) and isort
- Use type hints for all functions
- Document with NumPy-style docstrings
- Prefer reproducible experiments with fixed seeds
- Log all experiments with wandb or MLflow
- Version datasets and models with DVC or MLflow

